OTTAWA/CALGARY – Canadian Finance Minister Jim Flaherty said on Wednesday he knew of no direct talks between Ottawa and Beijing about making approval of CNOOC Ltd’s bid for Nexen Inc conditional on the approval of Canadian deals in China.<br />
